{"tid":2261650,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人既FD好鍾意冇啦啦講句動漫台詞","createTime":"2020-10-28T13:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T12:13:36.000Z","uid":127425,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce695a66d0c48fd68d8829425558f85de608eba","tid":2261650,"uid":127425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"今日同個FD係圖書館溫書<br />\n佢叫我幫佢睇下答得岩唔岩<br />\n我就話佢呢題寫錯左<br />\n佢跟住就話 &quot;錯既唔係我, 係呢個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot; <br />\n我聽完之後O哂嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一時之間比唔到反應<br />\n5秒之後我先feel到起哂雞皮<br />\n我見到對面果兩個妹妹仔黯住半邊嘴笑<br />\n毒撚真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b35f4f4ece1eadb10b080c46adde2cd52de5b81","tid":2261650,"uid":231583,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aabe14cebbe60f3c23651f3a7f74528c502722fa","tid":2261650,"uid":112760,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"El Psy Kongroo"},{"pid":"f8eca86b6212d47061918fd1a8e4d8d05ea786bd","tid":2261650,"uid":160447,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"aabe14cebbe60f3c23651f3a7f74528c502722fa","tid":2261650,"uid":112760,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"El Psy Kongroo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"嘟嘟嚕～"},{"pid":"99d55f5e0c35f4488b6c6ed14c1c3f740fd53ad8","tid":2261650,"uid":262886,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:01:19.000Z","msg":"識有個小妺妹每句嘢之後都會加咪啪^_^<br />\n夜晚仲會自言自話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},